{"tid":2089500,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"德語媒體：\"港版國安法說明北京的承諾不值得信賴\"","createTime":"2020-07-01T16:49:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-02T00:39:03.000Z","uid":179729,"like":145,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"0127fe27e3d3fe9b979c3d23ba2c14b81e0478e1","tid":2089500,"uid":179729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T16:49:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.dw.com/image/53992324_303.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fimage%2F53992324_303.jpg&h=08e72429&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《南德意志報》駐京記者Lea Deuber就中國人大常委會通過港版國安法一事撰寫並發表評論&quot;陷入恐懼中的城市&quot;（ Stadt in Angst ）。她在評論中指出，北京打破同英國之間簽訂的《聯合聲明》出台執行港版國安法，這說明&quot;將中國納入世界秩序的嘗試失敗了，而（北京）應為此承擔後果&quot;。<br />\n<br />\n德國左翼報紙《日報》也就港版國安法發表評論--&quot;向世界吹響起床的號角&quot;（ F&uuml;r die Welt ein Weckruf ）。評論認為，北京無視一份具有國際法效力的條約，取消香港的自治地位。國際社會不能不讓北京承擔後果。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n全文：<a href=\"https://dw.com/p/3edph\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdw.com%2Fp%2F3edph&d=Ia4lQUE8yf8cF0bf%2B23B9Sq0XD4M5CHb8byFtBYuAsM%3D&h=d342be0d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://dw.com/p/3edph</a><br />\n<br />\nFacebook：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/dw.chinese.traditional/posts/918411451994832\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fdw.chinese.traditional%2Fposts%2F918411451994832&d=Ia4lQUE8yf8cF0bf%2B23B9Sq0XD4M5CHb8byFtBYuAsM%3D&h=09513d09\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/dw.chinese.traditional/posts/918411451994832</a>"},{"pid":"cae0d58740d26bae52e9250f0133b03ee70a7b47","tid":2089500,"uid":179729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T17:00:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0af864bf9acdaecbfdd8587106b1de50cba424ce","tid":2089500,"uid":150930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T17:00:58.000Z","msg":"Dw"},{"pid":"c0b5e6bea95144ae28cb689ba490e11536dd293a","tid":2089500,"uid":21545,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"c